<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٤٨٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4108">عُبَيْدُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1611">أَبُو أُسَامَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«مَا غِرْتُ عَلَى امْرَأَةٍ مَا غِرْتُ عَلَى خَدِيجَةَ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَقَدْ أَمَرَهُ رَبُّهُ أَنْ يُبَشِّرَهَا بِبَيْتٍ فِي الْجَنَّةِ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>